The treatment variable in the regression varies within some group * period cells.
The results in de Chaisemartin, C. and D'Haultfoeuille, X. (2020) apply to two-way fixed effects regressions
with a group * period level treatment.
The command will replace the treatment by its average value in each group * period.
The results below apply to the two-way fixed effects regression with that treatment variable.

The control variable 1 varies within some group * period cells.
The results in de Chaisemartin, C. and D'Haultfoeuille, X. (2020) on two-way fixed effects regressions
with controls apply to group * period level controls.
The command will replace control variable 1 by its average value in each group * period cell.
The results below apply to the regression with control variable 1 averaged at the group * period level.


